==English==

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|la|abhorrens|abhorrēns, abhorrēntis}}, present active participle of {{m|la|abhorreō||abhor}}. See [[abhor]]

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/æbˈɔɹ.ənt/|lang=en}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/æbˈhɔɹ.ənt/|/æbˈhɑɹ.ənt/|lang=en}}

